Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:28.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That dish sure looks good, doesn’t it, Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:31.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:36.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis, for dinner, I cooked noodle soup.
