Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give it to Karasuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is! This is it!
