Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So is everybody here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.39,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}Yagami Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? I fixed my special box lunches for each of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Takano-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sawachika-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Tsukamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:41.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Nara, Imadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:52.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I made this one with\Nspecial care! Yakumo-kun, for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Deelish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:07.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Hanai-kun is a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:12.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. Don’t get depressed just\Nbecause Yakumo didn’t come. Okay, Hanai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my own lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima, give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:25.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I missed breakfast today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme… gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic can he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.41,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Travelling Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh. Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rooms are separated by sliding doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Urk! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re gonna change. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure. I wouldn’t open the door, would I? Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon! Let’s change, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got my shorts on underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:04.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori! Your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t expect me\Nto keep it, do you? Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?! Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your suit looks so adult, Akira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t mine pretty daring, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan’s boobs really\Nare big, aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your suit’s cute, too, Tsukamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It’s a different color from Yakumo’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo’s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For Yakumo’s sake, I can’t\Nallow any shameful behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach! So many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud. Hanai made me miss it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo, why didn’t you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, got any sunscreen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some. I’ll rub it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll get my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where’s Harima?
