Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so sure I’d brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A rugged spirit is calling to my wild side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got no time for foolishness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now… my trunks are?
