Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don’t scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a perfectly innocent situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she screams, I’ll look like a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Tenma-chan will think so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did I grab her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It came out all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s struggling like crazy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta explain! That I never\Nmeant for this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyhow, first, I gotta calm her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How? Uhh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now somebody’s coming! It’s all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn’t find your swimming trunks,\Nbut you went ahead and stripped anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You still couldn’t find them,\Nand Eri walked in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,so you panicked and tried to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,but ended up pinioning her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a total screw-up, Harima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong? Did you find the sunscreen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t have a chance to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s split the watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan! Let’s split the watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan! Miko-chan!\NMiko-chan’s drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hanai-kun took off his glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you’d be forced to swim if you went farther out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:47.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just like a lifeguard, Hanai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just used to saving her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some hot coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re lucky you can\Nswim like that, Hanai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,None of us girls can swim.\NRight, Eri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:07.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish is granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let’s go all-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming lessons start now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Let’s just\Nhave him teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a good teacher, too, right, Nara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I-I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! We men will be the teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I’m feeling the enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Yakumo’s not here, I couldn’t\Nsee any reason to come to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. By teaching her, I can\Nstart talking to her naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I’m gonna be the one\Nto teach Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So first, I’ll have to…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:50.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Imadori, you like the flashy type,\Nso you teach the flashy rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:51.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:57.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Hanai, you seem to be friends\Nwith Suou, so you teach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, um… uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:06.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t really stand out,\Nso teach that quiet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so draw up a chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re hopeless. Okay, I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everybody!\NWe’re assigning our partners!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:33.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let’s start the lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Mikoto-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be counting on your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Harima-kun be a complete idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:46.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed by one line…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:50.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over my dead body.
