Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… If you’ll allow me,\NI shall teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sawachika-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, give me your hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, your hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your han—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:45.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like that. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaguely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C’mon, c’mon…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how far do we have to go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let’s go as far as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me, Nara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s do our best, Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll use this chance to really get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s get started then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… S-Sure!
