Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:29.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. This is fair warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:33.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you’re getting to\Nteach Ten—, I mean, Tsukamoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,don’t get any weird desires or hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And… don’t fall for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:45.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like Tsukamoto, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can get close to her\Nbefore he can complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:57.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Maybe if I let go,\Nshe might stick even closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to let go for a while, now, Tsukamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Sure. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?! She’s swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:09.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! That’s enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I can swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe it all to you, Nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-chan! Aren’t you going swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai-kun’s worn himself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:31.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit staring, creep!\NI’ll squash you, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hopeless! Nothing’s working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun’s watching me like a hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He really scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe all I can do is watch…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Lost swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto! Did it come off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m scared of Harima-kun, but if\NI don’t go, I won’t be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Tsukamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Tsukamoto’s swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:14.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll retrieve this swimsuit…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,For you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:20.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geeze, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn’t it lucky that Nara\Nfound your trunks for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re marooned!
