Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:30.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t say that! I don’t\Nwanna die, Mikoto-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t wanna die, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And don’t use this as an excuse\Nto call me “Mikoto-chan”!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori! You can swim, can’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you swim to the shore somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You mean, stamina-wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:49.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things in the ocean. They scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come for?!\NJust to hit on girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t swim, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could I would swim home\Nand leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nothing else to do…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s try to think of a way to get\Nhelp from the people on the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:10.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking’s what I do best.\NI’ll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:12.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
