Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal fire would be the best…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No fire, though. Nothing to burn, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:21.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose were you planning to burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:27.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’d start with the one\Nthat has two pieces, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We might find something in this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s split up and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all he can think of,\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. What’s it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, we always see it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put a letter in it and float it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp4\frz0\t(0,525,\frz20)\an5\fad(0,1400)\fscx100\fscy100\t(\fscx300\fscy300)\c&H607BEF&\b0\fnCartonsix NC\fs60\pos(183,56)}BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:57.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’ll take years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot. No pencil.\NWe should write in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! We can’t be\Nfooling around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, I’m dead serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what to do?
