Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Plan D — Ride on the back of that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:43.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D seems like the most practical way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can’t place lmadori in danger all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’ll I do? I can’t think of anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:57.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Imadori’s thinking astonishlngly hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:04.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Any luck? Any good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with four\Npossibilities, from A to D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:09.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he think of the same idea as me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and come to the same conclusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He even chose D, the most dangerous plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:25.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m kind of… impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gotta be D.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:30.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a D-cup, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that right, Mikoto-ch—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2.5\fsp4\frz0\t(0,525,\frz20)\an5\fad(0,1400)\fscx100\fscy100\t(\fscx300\fscy300)\c&H607BEF&\b0\fnCartonsix NC\fs60\pos(428,119)}Pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:44.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto sure is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is, how do I suggest to her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,that I’ll swim if she gives me a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:55.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Mikoto-chan, do you like any guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:59.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Better forget the kiss, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like the faithful type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:06.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… What’s he like?\NDoes he go to our school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… He was an upperclassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in my 1st year, he was in his 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:15.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He graduated and attends\Na school in Tokyo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s a really smart guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get into the same college, but it’s really tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:27.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… There’s still hope.\NThis arrangement won’t last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you trying to get out of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I already heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:38.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, that’s why I can’t\Nbe wasting my time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need to\Nchange the subject back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:44.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't figured out\Nhow to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:49.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know… Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve got friends we can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know they’ll find us, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:05.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we go back to the inn,\Nlet’s take a picture together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:08.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A group picture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:16.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes… What do mice like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:16.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:20.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that\Nwe’ve forgotten something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:31.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs30\bord3\3c&HFFFBF1&\fnMercurius CT Std Medium\c&HF782ED&\pos(542,51)}They forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\bord3\fad(500,0)\pos(26,16)\b1\c&H609BE4&\3c&HE9EFF0&\fnTriplexBold}And they’re in\Na party mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:54.28,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:22:00.04,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:04.74,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:10.21,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.83,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:17.50,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.89,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:23.74,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:28.18,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.32,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:34.51,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:40.52,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.53,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:49.44,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.44,0:22:50.42,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:09.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Miko-chan! Where were you\Nand lmadori-kun all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Harima-kun’s in a horrible mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:15.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Miko-chan be the girl\Nthat Harima likes?!
